body:
# YMBD

YMDB (stands for Yagouus Movie DataBase) is a web app that interacts with [TMDB](https://www.themoviedb.org/). 
It's being developed with HTML5, CSS3 and AngularJS. Soon it will be transformed into a Cordova app.

Stay tuned.
